author: Ken Dilanian and Courtney Kube
title: U.S. intel community examining whether coronavirus emerged accidentally from a Chinese lab
description: U.S. officials say it's possible, but not the most likely explanation, that a Chinese lab worker could have become infected with COVID-19, then left the lab.
content:
WASHINGTON The U.S. intelligence community is examining whether the virus that caused a global pandemic emerged accidentally from a Chinese research lab studying diseases in bats, current and former U.S. intelligence officials tell NBC News.
